{"tid":220904,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"計劃緊八月尾去台灣，各位有冇咩景點個啲介紹？","createTime":"2017-04-28T09:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:11:22.000Z","uid":107388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a21f380b518bb2dd354e4be6373b9c67f761e6d","tid":220904,"uid":107388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"諗住去7日，自由行，諗緊自唔自駕埋，站時plan左小小行程，係墾丁玩兩日，跟住就去高雄玩一至兩日，最後就台中，有時間想落埋台南，因家父想去睇劍獅。<br />\n<br />\n墾丁就諗住去潛個水(因為岩岩考到個o仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，騎個馬，同玩下啲沙灘車個啲，仲有諗住去埋個水族管，<br />\n<br />\n高雄就仲未諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台中就站時諗住去清境同新起個個小型賽車場玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但諗緊咁樣會唔會好趕？？<br />\n<br />\n同各位有冇咩好介紹？？<br />\n例如民宿呀，食野呀，景點同shopping地點？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e88d2ccc34577fde17113bf8a541f7413bb49f","tid":220904,"uid":107388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T11:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dc4e23df6027829a03d1c6c675213b594ebb821","tid":220904,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"去嘅地方有啲似，留個名先"},{"pid":"51d984b667d984476de6dfc007519a7db6d0bc0f","tid":220904,"uid":107388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去嘅地方有啲似，留個名先</blockquote><br />\n巴打諗住幾時去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}